{"tid":1481184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[818/推上國際] 你班人唔出黎，對唔對得住呢個小朋友？","createTime":"2019-08-17T15:13:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T00:36:09.000Z","uid":162590,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"257623db1c612bb39b475352a6a7cdc64c200a62","tid":1481184,"uid":162590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T15:13:12.000Z","msg":"記住，我地應承過小朋友啲咩。<br />\n<br />\n我哋唔會再比小朋友要面對極權既黑暗。<br />\n<br />\n我地唔會再比小朋友圍繞既話題係，<br />\n黑警，催淚彈，橡膠子彈，布袋彈，<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可，光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n<br />\n我地唔會比小朋友要上街，去著gear，去抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢一代既責任，呢一代去背負，去完成。<br />\n<br />\n當你覺得好攰想放棄想偷懶既時候，<br />\n記住，我地應承過小朋友啲咩。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YCgtfMn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYCgtfMn.jpg&h=f8d0fb78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">818 兩點 維園見<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n612<br />\n721<br />\n811</span></span>"},{"pid":"0c08f858e6fb6edf8c1cf7acdf5754dfd5ef824a","tid":1481184,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T15:13:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a7663200f9c1ad68aa385f83cd5d44630442bc1","tid":1481184,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T15:14:33.000Z","msg":"818維園見！所有聽日去嘅人都同我入一入嚟！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1480894\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1480894</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5477c37958d672af1564afa25ccd4f033d4d3168","tid":1481184,"uid":162590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T15:15:00.000Z","msg":"818 兩點 維園見<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可<br />\n光復香港<br />\n